1. Checkout the package

2. Run init-autotools.sh

3. Copy the libsvm-2.8.tar.gz into the package and untar it. If a new
   libsvm verion should be used, change the paths in the rnaz/Makefile.am

4. Generate manual: change in doc, run makedoc.pl, TeX the manual.tex to a
   pdf and copy manual.pdf into the root directory of the package

5. Generate RNAz man-page using "pod2man RNAz.pod > RNAz.1" in man directory

6. Adjust the version numbers in configure.ac, perl/RNAz.pm

7. Update README, NEWS, TODO

9. Run  cvs2cl.pl which creates the ChanceLog file automatically.

10. Create a tag in CVS:  cvs tag -R rel-1-0

11. make dist

12. Copy tarball to win-RNAz dir and untar it. Cross compile it using 
    ../cross-configure.sh and ../cross-make.sh

13. Under Windows: Open "Advanced Installer Package" RNAz.aip and add updated
    files. Make the MSI installer package.

14. Update Website. If documentation has changed don't forget HTML documentation.    

